build/
samples/*.jpg
samples/*.jpeg
samples/*.png
samples/*.bmp
samples/*.tiff
samples/*.webp
!samples/.gitkeep

# Ship the downloader script and the license file so users see the
# licensing story without having to run the script. The actual
# images are produced by `python download_samples.py` and stay
# gitignored — no binaries in the repo.
!samples/download_samples.py
!samples/LICENSES.md
